St Jones Wort Sensei! Bergamot Sensei!
Hehe, listen to me, listen to me!

[px]!
You've mastered all the four elements of alchemy!

Oh! You've mastered four elements of alchemy
when you're this young...

Hehe, you remind me of Bergamot when she was young.

Indeed...
But I'm not aspirant as [px].

After all, [px] decides to synthesize
the "Pyroxene of Wisdom"!

basic requirement of synthesizing the "Pyroxene of Wisdom".

Keep trying and don't slacken off.

So I have to try harder to catch up with them——

Wow, Bergamot Sensei, you're smiling!
It's creepy! What's going on!?

What? I'm creepy!?
It's just a smile...!

Sigh——
If only I could help you a bit...

Excuse me, are you a student?
I need to see [px] for something...

Huh? Ah, yes, I'm junior to [px].
What can I do for you?

Oh, great.
Could you please take a message for me...

... Huh? Wistyria?
What is she and Bill Berry talking about...?
